# DIRT
 
WE WILL COLLECT ORGANIC WASTE LOCALLY ALONG THE TRASH MAGIC NETWORK VIA THE SHOPPING CARTS AND CREATE COMPOST REACTORS WHICH FORM NEW FRESH SOIL!

WE WILL MOVE THE SOIL AROUND ON THE STREET NETWORK AND WATERSHED NETWORK!

THE DIRT WILL BE CONNECTED TO THE SENSORS WHICH STREAM THE DATA OF WHAT IS  HAPPENING IN THE LIVING SOIL, MAKING THE SOIL INTO A CYBERNETIC SUPER ORGANISM!

USE CHEAP DIGITAL MICROSCOPES TO TAKE VIDEO DATA OF SOIL!

GET CHEAP SPECTROMETERS TO TRACK ION CONCENTRATION IN THE SOIL!  

SHARE THE DATA OVER THE TRASH MAGIC WEB!

THE SCIENTIFIC COMMUNITY ON THE TRASH MAGIC NETWORK THEN JOINS FORCES TO ANALYZE THE DATA AND FEED IT BACK TO OUR CHOICES OF WHAT TO DO WITH THE LIVING SOIL!


WE WILL GUIDE THE EVOLUTION OF THE CYBERNETIC SUPER ORGANISM THAT IS THE GLOBAL NETWORK OF THE LIVING SOIL COMBINED WITH THE TRASH MAGIC NETWORK!

WE WILL BUILD BILLIONS OF TONS OF SOIL EVERY YEAR!

ALL THE SOIL WILL STREAM DATA ON THE GLOBAL NETWORK!

ALL THE DATA WILL FEED BACK TO THE SOIL!

WE WILL ALL BECOME A PART OF THE GLOBAL SOIL NETWORK!

ALONG WITH OUR MACHINES OF MEDIA!
 
